# App Router only — no pages/ folder

This project uses **Next.js App Router** exclusively (`app/` folder).

## NEVER do this

- Create a `pages/` folder
- Create any file under `pages/`, including:
  - `pages/_document.js`
  - `pages/_app.js`
  - `pages/index.js`
  - Any other Pages Router file

## ALWAYS do this

- Put routes in `app/` (e.g. `app/page.js`, `app/layout.js`, `app/project/[id]/page.js`)
- Use `app/layout.js` for root layout and theme scripts — not `_document.js`

## If pages/ is created by mistake

Delete the entire `pages/` folder immediately.
